{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "gymgate-api-explorer-v1",
    "name": "GymGate API – Explorer",
    "description": "# GymGate API Explorer\n\nKolekcja do ręcznego eksplorowania API. Zawiera wszystkie endpointy pogrupowane tematycznie.\n\n## Konfiguracja\n\nUstaw zmienne środowiskowe lub collection variables:\n- `baseUrl` – domyślnie `http://localhost:3000`\n- `loginEmail` / `loginPassword` – dane do auto-logowania\n\n## Auto-auth\n\nPre-request script na poziomie kolekcji automatycznie pobiera token JWT przed każdym requestem (jeśli `authToken` jest pusty). Wystarczy ustawić `loginEmail` i `loginPassword`.\n\n## Uruchomienie backendu lokalnie\n```bash\ncd backend && npm run dev\n```",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:3000", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "authToken", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "userId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "loginEmail", "value": "test@gymgate.pl", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "loginPassword", "value": "TestPass123", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "exerciseId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "workoutId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "workoutItemId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "setId", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "const token = pm.collectionVariables.get('authToken');",
          "if (token && token.length > 10) return;",
          "",
          "const baseUrl = pm.collectionVariables.get('baseUrl');",
          "const email = pm.collectionVariables.get('loginEmail');",
          "const password = pm.collectionVariables.get('loginPassword');",
          "",
          "if (!email || !password) {",
          "  console.warn('Brak loginEmail / loginPassword – ustaw collection variables');",
          "  return;",
          "}",
          "",
          "pm.sendRequest({",
          "  url: baseUrl + '/api/auth/login',",
          "  method: 'POST',",
          "  header: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },",
          "  body: { mode: 'raw', raw: JSON.stringify({ email, password }) }",
          "}, (err, res) => {",
          "  if (err || res.code !== 200) {",
          "    console.warn('Auto-login nieudany:', err || res.status());",
          "    return;",
          "  }",
          "  const json = res.json();",
          "  pm.collectionVariables.set('authToken', json.data.token);",
          "  pm.collectionVariables.set('userId', json.data.user.id);",
          "  console.log('Auto-login OK, userId:', json.data.user.id);",
          "});"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
